AWS Budgets manages and controls your billing on AWS, it is the simplest way on AWS to track your spend.
The alerts are also set such that through your set threshold, whenever you have exceeded or are about to exceed your budget, you will recieve a notification through email or any other means.
It can be set to monthly, annually etc.

STEPS TO THIS
Go to AWS budgets
Click on Bugdets
Create new budget
Set your threshold
Configure your alerts, input your mail address
Select other options if required and complete the process of creating the budget
